name: Experiment Or Die #65
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. I love science-fiction! I love it. There are endless narratives that span the entire spectrum of your imagination. In some dreamscape of my own I'd imagined myself as a space-cowboy riding a lizard mount through a ghost town on a distant planet. Signs of the bygone civilization everywhere but I don't stop to wait for any stirrings of actual life. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
